"{\"uid\": \"news.sky.com-story-far-left-activist-arrested-over-railway-attacks-ahead-of-paris-olympics-13185452\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Landline and mobile services were affected following the attack on France's telecoms network, which comes days after vandals used explosive devices to set off fires on major railway lines around the country.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 207, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 8, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Landline\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.101941084710128e-45, \"text\": \"Landline\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Landline\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Landline\"}, {\"begin\": 67, \"end\": 73, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.1940851178844292e-12, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Monday 29 July 2024 12:39, UK  France's telecoms network has suffered isolated outages across the country after being targeted by vandals, with 11,000 customers affected.\", \"from\": 209, \"to\": 379, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 236, \"end\": 238, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999994891842502, \"rank\": 5.1042463606355e-07, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 240, \"end\": 246, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.1940851178844292e-12, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Marina Ferrari, junior minister for digital matters said in a post on social media platform X some landline and mobile services were affected following the overnight attacks.\", \"from\": 381, \"to\": 555, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I condemn in the strongest terms these cowardly and irresponsible acts,\\\" she wrote.\", \"from\": 557, \"to\": 641, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Thank you to the teams mobilised this morning to carry out repairs and restore damaged sites to service.\\\"\", \"from\": 643, \"to\": 749, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Frenchmedia reports on Monday said telecom installations belonging to companies SFR, Bouygues Telecom and Free had been vandalised, affecting mainly fixed-line services.\", \"from\": 751, \"to\": 920, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 836, \"end\": 852, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bouygues_Telecom\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bouygues Telecom\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bouygues_Telecom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bouygues_Telecom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The reports in Le Parisien newspaper and BFM TV said cables in electrical cabinets had been cut in southern France, and that installations in the Meuse region near Luxembourg and the Oise area near Paris had also been targeted.\", \"from\": 922, \"to\": 1149, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 937, \"end\": 948, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Le_Parisien\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Le Parisien\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Le_Parisien\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Le_Parisien\"}, {\"begin\": 963, \"end\": 969, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BFM_TV\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"BFM TV\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BFM_TV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BFM_TV\"}, {\"begin\": 1030, \"end\": 1036, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, 