pedia.org/resource/Autorit\\u00e9_de_R\\u00e9gulation_des_Communications_\\u00c9lectroniques,_des_Postes_et_de_la_Distribution_de_la_Presse\"}, {\"begin\": 1222, \"end\": 1225, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SFR\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.614167075280258e-35, \"text\": \"SFR\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SFR\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SFR\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A police official also said at least six of France's administrative departments were affected, including the region around the Mediterranean city of Marseille which is hosting football and sailing competitions for the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1245, \"to\": 1472, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1289, \"end\": 1295, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.1940851178844292e-12, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 1394, \"end\": 1403, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marseille\", \"score\": 0.9999999861674952, \"rank\": 1.379916667575731e-08, \"text\": \"Marseille\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marseille\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marseille\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It comes after reports said a far-left activist had been arrested in connection with a series of attacks on the country's high-speed train network which caused travel chaos ahead of theParis Olympicsopening ceremony.\", \"from\": 1474, \"to\": 1690, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please use Chrome browser for a more accessible video player    Follow Paris Olympics latest  Railway attack  France's interior minister Gerald Darmanin appeared to confirm media reports of an arrest being made on Sunday in Seine-Maritime, Normandy.\", \"from\": 1692, \"to\": 1941, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1802, \"end\": 1808, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.1940851178844292e-12, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 1829, \"end\": 1835, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gerald_Ford\", \"score\": 0.9999132314489824, \"rank\": 8.48246658788934e-05, \"text\": \"Gerald\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gerald_Ford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gerald_Ford\"}, {\"begin\": 1916, \"end\": 1930, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Maritime\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Seine-Maritime\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Maritime\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Maritime\"}, {\"begin\": 1932, \"end\": 1940, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Normandy_landings\", \"score\": 0.8839187941535321, \"rank\": 0.13132161218083346, \"text\": \"Normandy\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Normandy_landings\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Normandy_landings\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the Paris prosecutor's office said it was unconnected to the disruption on Friday - and that no one has been arrested so far in the national investigation into the arson attacks.\", \"from\": 1943, \"to\": 2125, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1951, \"end\": 1956, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9915706233566044e-23, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was not immediately clear if the telecoms vandalism was connected to the railway attack which marred the start of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 2127, \"to\": 2257, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Vandals used explosive devices to set off fires which damaged signal boxes along lines connecting the capital with cities such as Lille in the north, Bordeaux in the west and Strasbourg in the east, state-owned railway operator SNCF said.\", \"from\": 2259, \"to\": 2497, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2389, \"end\": 2394, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lille\", \"score\": 0.9999999290121221, \"rank\": 7.08245394093287e-08, \"text\": \"Lille\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lille\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lille\"}, {\"begin\": 2434, \"end\": 2444, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Strasbourg-Ville_station\", \"score\": 0.9865424693127512, \"rank\": 0.013641106293691366, \"text\": \"Strasbourg\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Strasbourg-Ville_station\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Strasbourg-Ville_station\"}, {\"begin\": 2487, \"end\": 2491, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SNCF\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"SNCF\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SNCF\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SNCF\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Another attack on the Paris-Marseille line was foiled.\", \"from\": 2499, \"to\": 2553, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Keep up with all the latest news from the UK and around the world by following Sky News  Hundreds of thousands of people were left stranded at stations afterthe overnight attackson the TGV network which authorities called coordinated sabotage.\", \"from\": 2555, \"to\": 2798, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2597, \"end\": 2599, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999994891842502, \"rank\": 5.1042463606355e-07, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 2634, 